title: TradingView Chart Integration
tags: [[GettingStarted]] [[AI Supply Chain]]
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The AI supply-chain node tiddlers now include embedded TradingView charts when a ticker can be mapped to a TradingView symbol.

Implementation notes:

* Uses TradingView's iframe widget URL, not an external script, because TiddlyWiki blocks `script` tags as unsafe.
* Each node keeps its illustrative ticker list in the `tickers` field.
* Nodes with a recognized ticker also get a `tradingview-symbol` field.
* The chart is illustrative and defaults to the first recognized ticker for that node.

Examples:

* [[AI Supply Chain: AI Accelerators]]
* [[AI Supply Chain: Hyperscalers / Cloud Providers]]
* [[AI Supply Chain: Lithography Tools]]
* [[AI Supply Chain: Electric Grid]]

Ticker/company lists are examples only, not investment advice.
